gin="5" Size="8" Leading="9" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify">This enactment amends the <I>Navigable Waters Protection Act </I>in order to add Minnow Lake and other lakes and waterways to the navigable waters listed in the schedule to that Act, as it will read immediately after the coming into force of section 331 of the <I>Jobs and Growth Act, 2012</I>.</Para></Block></Bill_Part><Bill_Part Part_Type="MainText" CountLines="Yes" RunningHead_E="Navigable Waters Protection (Minnow Lake and other lakes and waterways)"><Block Align="Yes"><Para Style="MainText_DocNo">412044</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Style="Session_Reign">2nd Session, 41st Parliament,</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Style="Session_Reign">62 Elizabeth II, 2013</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Style="MainBillOrigin">house of commons of canada</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Bold="Yes" Style="MAIN@BillNo_Title">BILL C-554</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Style="MAIN@ti;04">An Act to amend the Navigable Waters Protection Act (Minnow Lake and other lakes and waterways)</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><Para LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify">Her Majesty, by and with the advice and consent of the Senate and House of Commons of Canada, enacts as follows:</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes" KeepWith="Next"><!--Heading:NAVIGABLE WATERS PROTECTION ACT--><MarginalNote>R.S., c. N-22<br /></MarginalNote><Para TopMargin="10" Hyphenate="OFF" TextAlign="Center"><B>NAVIGABLE WATERS PROTECTION ACT</B></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2" Bold="Yes"><B>1.</B> (1) Part 1 of the schedule to the <I>Navigable Waters Protection Act</I>, as it reads immediately after the coming into force of section 331 of the <I>Jobs and Growth Act, 2012</I>, is amended by adding after item 28 in the columns shown the following:</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Item: 芒聙聹28.1芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 1: 芒聙聹Minnow Lake芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 2: 芒聙聹47脗掳38芒聙虏12芒聙鲁 N, 82脗掳57芒聙虏35芒聙鲁 W芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 3: 芒聙聹The lake芒聙聶s water boundary includes the mouths of all connecting waterways芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2" Bold="Yes">(2) Part 1 of the schedule to the Act is amended by adding after item 29 in the columns shown the following:<PageBreak /></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Item: 芒聙聹29.1芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 1: 芒聙聹Ramsey Lake芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 2: 芒聙聹47脗掳15芒聙虏02芒聙鲁 N, 82脗掳15芒聙虏25芒聙鲁 W芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 3: 芒聙聹The lake芒聙聶s water boundary includes the mouths of all connecting waterways芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Item: